<?xml version="1.0"?>
<rdf:RDF xmlns="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#"
     xml:base="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl"
     xmlns:iso="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#"
     xmlns:owl="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#"
     xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"
     xmlns:xml="http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace"
     xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#"
     xmlns:rdfs="http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#"
     xmlns:skos="http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#"
     xmlns:owl2xml="http://www.w3.org/2006/12/owl2-xml#">

    <owl:Ontology rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl">
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Corpus examples in English representing various relations of the ISO ontology (ISO 24617-8).</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Ontology>

<!-- CAUSE -->

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>Perhaps because they won, Mr. Bork’s attackers come through more vividly than his defenders.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 1</skos:notation>

    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_Perhaps_because_1">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>Perhaps because</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_1">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>they won</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_1">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>Mr. Bork’s attackers come through more vividly than his defenders</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_2">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>Sears is negotiating to refinance its Sears Tower for close to $850 million, sources said. because The retailer was unable to find a buyer for the building.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 2</skos:notation>

    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_2">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>Sears  is  negotiating  to  refinance  its  Sears  Tower  for  close  to  $850  million</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_because_2">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>because</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_2">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>The retailer was unable to find a buyer for the building</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_3">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>Now, though, enormous costs for earthquake relief will pile on top of outstanding costs for hurricane relief. “That obviously means that we won’t have enough for all of the emergencies that are now facing us, and we will have to consider appropriate requests for follow-on funding,” Mr. Fitzwater said.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 3</skos:notation>

    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_3">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>Now, though, enormous costs for earthquake relief will pile on top of outstanding costs  for hurricane relief</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_That_obviously_means_3">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>That obviously means</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_3">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>we won’t have enough for all of the emergencies  that are now facing us, and we will have to consider appropriate requests for follow-on funding</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_4">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>The nations of southern Africa know a lot about managing elephants; as their herds are thriving.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 4</skos:notation>

    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_4">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>The nations of southern Africa know a lot about managing elephants</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_as_4">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>as</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_4">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>their  herds are thriving</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_5">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>What makes people blurt out their credit-card numbers to a caller they’ve never heard of? Do they really believe that the number is just for verification and is simply a formality on the road to being a grand-prize winner? What makes a person buy an oil well from some stranger knocking on the screen door? Or an interest in a retirement community in Nevada that will knock your socks off, once it is built? Because in the end, these people always wind up asking themselves the same question: “How could I be so stupid?”</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 5</skos:notation>

    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_5">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>What makes people blurt out their credit-card numbers to a caller they’ve never heard of?  Do they really believe that the number is just for verification and is simply a formality on the road  to being a grand-prize winner? What makes a person buy an oil well from some stranger knocking  on the screen door? Or an interest in a retirement community in Nevada that will knock your socks  off, once it is built?</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_Because_5">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>Because</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_5">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>in the end, these people always wind up asking themselves the  same question: “How could I be so stupid</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_6">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>My favourite is the police department. because They’re not aimed at the criminal. The judicial system is aimed at the citizens.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 6</skos:notation>

    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_6">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>My  favourite  is  the  police  department</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_because_6">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>because</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasReason>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Reason_6">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Reason"/>
            <rdfs:label>They’re  not  aimed  at  the  criminal</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasReason>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Cause_7">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Cause"/>
    <rdfs:label>U: I thought well from like Elmira through to Corning to Bath is how many hours? S: four hours U: so we’re like screwed as far as those two box cars at Bath.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 7</skos:notation>

    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_U_I_thought_well_from_like_Elmira_through_to_Corni_7">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>U: I thought well from like Elmira through to Corning to Bath is how many hours? S: four hours U: so</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasResult>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Result_7">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Result"/>
            <rdfs:label>we’re like screwed as far as those two box cars at Bath</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasResult>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<!-- CONDITION -->

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Condition">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Condition"/>
    <rdfs:label>But some bond market analysts said that could quickly change if property casualty insurance companies scramble to sell portions of their municipal portfolios to raise cash to pay damage claims.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 8</skos:notation>

    <hasConsequent>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Consequent_8">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Consequent"/>
            <rdfs:label>that could quickly change</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConsequent>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_if_8">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>if</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Condition_2">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Condition"/>
    <rdfs:label>If anyone has difficulty imagining a world in which history went merrily on without us, Mr. Gould sketches several.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 9</skos:notation>

    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_If_9">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>If</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasConsequent>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Consequent_9">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Consequent"/>
            <rdfs:label>Mr. Gould sketches several</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConsequent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<!-- NEGATIVE CONDITION -->

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_NegativeCondition">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#NegativeCondition"/>
    <rdfs:label>Unless the Federal Reserve eases interest rates soon to stimulate the economy, profits could remain disappointing.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 10</skos:notation>

    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_Unless_10">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>Unless</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_ConsequentOfNegativeCondition_10">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#ConsequentOfNegativeCondition"/>
            <rdfs:label>profits could  remain disappointing</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_NegativeCondition_2">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#NegativeCondition"/>
    <rdfs:label>But a Soviet bank here would be crippled unless Moscow found a way to settle the $188 million debt, which was lent to the country’s short-lived democratic Kerensky government before the Communists seized power in 1917.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 11</skos:notation>

    <hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_ConsequentOfNegativeCondition_11">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#ConsequentOfNegativeCondition"/>
            <rdfs:label>But a Soviet bank here would be crippled</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_unless_11">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>unless</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_NegativeCondition_3">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#NegativeCondition"/>
    <rdfs:label>If you cannot give me a fully convincing explanation here and now, you’re fired.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 12</skos:notation>

    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_If_12">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>If</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_ConsequentOfNegativeCondition_12">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#ConsequentOfNegativeCondition"/>
            <rdfs:label>you’re fired</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConsequentOfNegativeCondition>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<!-- PURPOSE -->

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Purpose">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Purpose"/>
    <rdfs:label>Skilled ringers use their wrists to advance or retard the next swing, so that one bell can swap places with another in the following change.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 13</skos:notation>

    <hasEnablement>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Enablement_13">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Enablement"/>
            <rdfs:label>Skilled ringers use their wrists to advance or retard the next swing</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasEnablement>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_so_that_13">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>so that</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasGoal>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Goal_13">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Goal"/>
            <rdfs:label>one bell can swap  places with another in the following change</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasGoal>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Purpose_2">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Purpose"/>
    <rdfs:label>Adjusters must count the number of bathrooms, balconies, fireplaces, chimneys, microwaves and dishwashers. But they must also assign a price to each of these items as well as to floors, wall coverings, roofing and siding, to come up with a total value for a house. To do that, they must think in terms of sheetrock by the square foot, carpeting by the square yard, wallpaper by the roll, moulding by the linear foot.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 14</skos:notation>

    <hasGoal>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Goal_14">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Goal"/>
            <rdfs:label>But they must also assign a price to each of these items as well as to  floors, wall coverings, roofing and siding, to come up with a total value for a house</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">1</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasGoal>
    <hasConnective>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Connective_To_do_that_14">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Connective"/>
            <rdfs:label>To  do that</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">2</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasConnective>
    <hasEnablement>
        <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Enablement_14">
            <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Enablement"/>
            <rdfs:label>they must think in terms of sheetrock by the square foot, carpeting by the square yard,  wallpaper by the roll, moulding by the linear foot</rdfs:label>
            <skos:order rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">3</skos:order>
        </owl:NamedIndividual>
    </hasEnablement>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<!-- MANNER -->

