<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.EN.owl#Example_Synchrony_3">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://purl.org/olia/discourse/discourse.ISO.UDisc.owl#Synchrony"/>
    <rdfs:label>The parishioners of St. Michael and All Angels stop to chat at the church door, as members here always have. while In the tower, five men and women pull rhythmically on ropes attached to the same five bells that first sounded here in 1614.</rdfs:label>

    <skos:notation>ISO-G 43</skos:notation>

    <hasArg1>
